[BDCFF]
Version=0.5

[game]
Name=Alchemyst Dangerdash Vol.6
Author=Alchemystics
Date=2025-11-19
Story=After finding inspiration from the third Myriad belonging to Ma'lankh, you get a message urging you to return to Moonspiral.\n\nThe last known location of Kaedra Lafore was discovered. She was known for her wild alchemy and research on the transmutative properties of zelar, a mysterious mineral that seems to have taken form of the myriad of gemstones you've encountered before. And as you no doubt have guessed, you're being sent to find just that, alongside any gemstones that might've been transmuted at the moment.\n\nAfter all, the scholars haven't figured out what value zelar has just yet. It's nothing but an inert material..

